OL,3,C100 years since the 'birth' of
OL,4,Ctelevision took place in Soho
OL,6,FA small room in Soho is being marked
OL,7,Fas the birthplace of television, 100
OL,8,Fyears after inventor John Logie Baird
OL,9,Fshowed moving images onscreen for the
OL,10,Ffirst time.
OL,12,FThe building where the experiment took
OL,13,Fplace is now home to Bar Italia, a
OL,14,Fpopular late-night coffee shop.
