OL,6,F"That was then turned into a radio
OL,7,Fwave and then transmitted across to a
OL,8,Fdisplay unit or a television"
OL,10,FFollowing John's discovery, London
OL,11,Fcontinued to play a central role in
OL,12,Ftelevision's development. A decade
OL,13,Flater, Alexandra Palace in North
OL,14,FLondon became the home of the world's
OL,15,Ffirst regular television broadcasts.
