OL,3,C100 years since the 'birth' of
OL,4,Ctelevision took place in Soho
OL,6,FKirsten Forrest is the Curatorial &
OL,7,FInterpretation Manager at Alexandra
OL,8,FPalace. She told ITV News London that
OL,9,FBaird unfortunately did not win the
OL,10,F"competition" for broadcasting live
OL,11,Ftelevision.
OL,13,FShe said: "There was a delay of about
OL,14,F54 seconds so it wasn't truly live.
OL,15,FThe pictures that they transmitted on
OL,16,Fthe Baird system were very good but it
OL,17,Fwas this element of them not being
OL,18,Flive that became the issue.
