OL,3,C100 years since the 'birth' of
OL,4,Ctelevision took place in Soho
OL,6,F"The engineers were quite frustrated
OL,7,Fwith it. They said it was like sending
OL,8,Fa telegram when you knew that there
OL,9,Fwas a telephone in the next room."
OL,11,FHowever, she agrees that Baird's
OL,12,Fdiscovery was "fundamental" to the
OL,13,Ffirst days of television.
OL,15,FIn 1936, the BBC began broadcasting
OL,16,Ffrom the site, allowing people to
OL,17,Fwatch television in their own homes
OL,18,Ffor the first time. Alexandra Palace
OL,19,Fis set to mark the 90th anniversary of
OL,20,Fthose broadcasts later this year.
